OL,6,FWatch Colette's story...
OL,8,FA woman who was just 17-years-old when
OL,9,Fshe was infected with products
OL,10,Ffollowing a routine operation has told
OL,11,FITV News she tried to take her own
OL,12,Flife.
OL,14,FColette Wintle, who's from
OL,15,FWorcestershire, contracted hepatitis
OL,16,FB, hepatitis C, and was exposed to
OL,17,FCreutzfeldt-Jakob Disease (CJD). The
OL,18,Fhepatitis infections led to severe
OL,19,Fliver damage, and three years ago,
OL,20,FColette was diagnosed with liver
OL,21,Fcancer.
