OL,6,FIt took 26 years for Colette to
OL,7,Fdiscover the devastating truth: she
OL,8,Fhad been given contaminated blood.J"I
OL,9,Fwish to have the name of the person
OL,10,Fwho specifically put in my records
OL,11,F'Factor 8' and crossed out 'safer
OL,12,Fproduct' which I was supposed to have
OL,13,Fbeen given," she said, reflecting on
OL,14,Fthe betrayal and lack of transparency
OL,15,Fthat marked her early experiences with
OL,16,Fthe healthcare system.JAt 23, Colette
OL,17,Funderwent another minor operation for
OL,18,Fback pain, during which she was
OL,19,Fexposed to hepatitis B.
