OL,6,FHer symptoms took six months to become
OL,7,Fvisible - during which time three
OL,8,Fdifferent GPs dismissed her concerns,
OL,9,Fsuggesting she was imagining them.
OL,11,FFortunately, the cancer was treatable,
OL,12,Fbut she acknowledges the grim reality
OL,13,Fshe faces. "I know that I'm facing the
OL,14,F'inevitable' and it's only a matter of
OL,15,Ftime," she said.JFor over three
OL,16,Fdecades, Colette has been a tireless
OL,17,Fcampaigner, seeking justice and truth
OL,18,Ffrom the government.
