OL,6,FHer battle has not been just for
OL,7,Fherself, but for the thousands of
OL,8,Fhaemophiliacs and their families
OL,9,Faffected by this scandal.
OL,11,FShe said: "At that point I realised
OL,12,Fthat I don't have a choice here I
OL,13,Feither stand up and speak out and
OL,14,Fstart campaigning or I sit back and do
OL,15,Fnothing and that that wasn't
OL,16,Facceptable to me I wanted the truth
OL,17,Ffact after effect after fact being
OL,18,Fpresented and you can't imagine the
OL,19,Ffrustration of being rejected every
OL,20,Ftime that you present the evidence."
