OL,6,FColette recalls the immense
OL,7,Ffrustration and repeated rejection she
OL,8,Ffaced in her quest for answers - as
OL,9,Fwell as the ripple effect of the
OL,10,Fcrisis.
OL,12,FShe highlights the widespread
OL,13,Fdevastation, adding: "Five members of
OL,14,Fone family were all infected at the
OL,15,Fsame time".
OL,17,FThe physical and emotional toll of her
OL,18,Fcondition has been profound. Colette
OL,19,Fdescribed the grueling experience of
OL,20,Fantiviral chemotherapy in 1999, which
OL,21,Fnearly killed her.
