OL,6,FDespite these challenges, she strived
OL,7,Fto provide a semblance of normalcy for
OL,8,Fher daughter, even as her own health
OL,9,Fdeteriorated.JThe lack of transparency
OL,10,Fand repeated cover-ups by the health
OL,11,Fauthorities have only added to
OL,12,FColette's ordeal.JColette's campaign
OL,13,Ffor justice is driven by a desire for
OL,14,Ftruth and accountability. "We put our
OL,15,Ftrust in the NHS, and we never thought
OL,16,Fthey would be capable of doing what
OL,17,Fthey've done to us," she said.
