OL,6,FDespite the government's apologies,
OL,7,Fshe insists that more is needed`an
OL,8,Facknowledgment of the specific wrongs
OL,9,Fand a commitment to real change.JHer
OL,10,Fhope is for peace and vindication for
OL,11,Fall those affected by the scandal. "I
OL,12,Fwish them peace and being able to move
OL,13,Fon," she says, longing for a time when
OL,14,Fshe and others can leave this painful
OL,15,Fchapter behind and enjoy the remaining
OL,16,Fyears of their lives.
OL,18,FHer fight continues, but so does her
OL,19,Fhope for justice and closure.
